                <div class="social-icons">
                    <a class="social-icon" href="https://github.com/Andrea301706"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                    <a class="social-icon" href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a class="social-icon" href="https://www.facebook.com/ara.andrea.roman.2025"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <hr class="m-0" />

        <!-- Experience Section -->
        <section class="resume-section" id="experience">
            <div class="resume-section-content">
                <h2 class="mb-5">Experience</h2>

                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between mb-5">
                    <div class="flex-grow-1">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">Student</h3>
                        <div class="subheading mb-3">Learning How to Code</div>
                        <p>
                            I am currently a student tackling Information Systems. My experience includes making programs even when I had no prior knowledge of coding. Now, I am learning and improving my skills. As a first-timer, I am exploring and trying to understand the basics.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-primary">September 2025 - Present</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <hr class="m-0" />

        <!-- Education Section -->
        <section class="resume-section" id="education">
            <div class="resume-section-content">
                <h2 class="mb-5">Education</h2>

                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between mb-5">
                    <div class="flex-grow-1">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">University of Nueva Caceres</h3>
                        <div class="subheading mb-3">Humanities and Social Sciences</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-primary">July 2023 - May 2024</span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between">
                    <div class="flex-grow-1">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">College of Subic Montessori Inc.</h3>
                        <div class="subheading mb-3">Information Systems</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-primary">September 2025 - Present</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <hr class="m-0" />

        <!-- Skills Section -->
        <section class="resume-section" id="skills">
            <div class="resume-section-content">
                <h2 class="mb-5">Skills</h2>
                <ul class="list-inline dev-icons">
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-html5"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-css3-alt"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-js-square"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-angular"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-react"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-node-js"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-sass"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-less"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-wordpress"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-gulp"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-grunt"></i></li>
                    <li class="list-inline-item"><i class="fab fa-npm"></i></li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="fa-ul mb-0">
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></span>Good in Communication</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></span>Critical Thinking</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></span>Decision Making</li>
                    <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></span>Leadership</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <hr class="m-0" />

        <!-- Projects Section -->
        <section class="resume-section" id="projects">
            <div class="resume-section-content">
                <h2 class="mb-5">Projects</h2>
                <p>
                    The project that we did in our school is planting, cooking, etc. That will be our mark as a project in school.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-0">
                    Aside from makeup, I love reading—especially about current trending topics like politics. As a Humanista, I stay aware of what's happening around the world. As a student, I also worry about how public funds are being used and misused. We need to be more aware of these issues.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <hr class="m-0" />

        <!-- Problem 3 Section -->
        <section class="resume-section" id="problem3">
            <div class="resume-section-content">
                <h2 class="mb-5">Problem 3</h2>

                <h3 class="mb-3">Calculate Average of Three Numbers</h3>

                <form method="post">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label asp-for="Number1" class="form-label">Number 1:</label>
                        <input asp-for="Number1" type="number" step="any" class="form-control" required />
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label asp-for="Number2" class="form-label">Number 2:</label>
                        <input asp-for="Number2" type="number" step="any" class="form-control" required />
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label asp-for="Number3" class="form-label">Number 3:</label>
                        <input asp-for="Number3" type="number" step="any" class="form-control" required />
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Calculate</button>
                </form>

                @if (Model.Average.HasValue)
                {
                    <div class="alert alert-success mt-3">
                        <strong>Average:</strong> @Model.Average.Value.ToString("F2")
                    </div>
                }
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap core JS-->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Core theme JS-->
    <script src="js/scripts.js"></script>
</body>
